<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Ry Jeso Tompo Avotray,
 Mitomoera aminay,
 Aidino ny Fanahinao,
 Tahio izahay izao.

[V2]
 Ny sitrakao mba ambarao
 Ho fantatray ny hevitrao ;
 Ny fonay amboaronao
 Hahay handray ny teninao.

[V3]
 Ny vavanay hasinonao
 Hahaizanay hisaotra Anao,
 Fa be ny soa azonay
 Nomenao, ry Mpanavotray.

[V4]
 Rahatrizay ny olonao
 Hihoby sy hidera Anao,
 Fa masina, fa masina,
 Fa masina i Jehovah.</lyrics>
<title>Ry Jeso Tompo, Avotray FFPM220</title>
<author>L. Mason</author>
<hymn_number>220</hymn_number>
</song>